title: Jurassic Park 4 - Jurassic World Trailer
description: New fan trailer for Jurassic Park 4 Jurassic World Staring Sam Neill, Laura Dern, Jeff Goldblum, Julianne Moore, Ariana Richards, Joseph Mazzello and a cameo by Vanessa Lee Chester This is a fan created trailer, the real film has been announced for a 2015 release. Music used was the Jurassic Park Jay30k Drumstep Remix. Check it out http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PAz5EO... The shots of Alan Grant are from the film The Hunter. Ellie Sattler clips are from the show Enlightened. The clips of Tim are from a short film called First Kiss. The shot of Lex was edited from an interview on the Jurassic Park Blu Ray. The clips of Ian Malcom are from a Hilton Hotels commercial. The clips of Sarah Harding are from the film The Forgotten. The single shot of Kelly is from a web series called 9ine. And as everyone has already stated, the dinosaurs are taken from Tera Nova
